The paper introduces a library for deep-learning-based time series modeling, which is a topic that spans multiple sub-categories in computer science. Based on the content of the abstract, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), as the paper focuses on simplifying the development and experimentation of time series models using deep learning. Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.ST (Statistics), and cs.CV (Computer Vision), as these sub-categories also cover topics related to time series modeling and deep learning.
